==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tasker
<hw>Task"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
imposes a task.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who performs a task, as a day-laborer.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A laborer who receives his wages in kind.</def>
<mark>[Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Taskmaster</ent>⟦br⟧
